FBIS4-56116 "dreeu103_k_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-103 Daily Report 26 May 1994 CROATIA Party of Rights Leaves Opposition Bloc Party of Rights Leaves Opposition Bloc LD2605201694 Zagreb HTV Television in Serbo-Croatian 1730 GMT 26 May 94 LD2605201694 Zagreb HTV Television Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] The extreme right-wing Croatian Party of Rights [Hrvatska Stranka Prava] has left the opposition bloc. However, according to its leaders, this does not mean that it will forge an alliance with the ruling party.
